social_posts.post_text: Rare picture of my older son C.J. who turned 20 years old in May! He started on #rhonj filming his 6th birthday! Where has the time gone? He rarely lets me posts pictures of him, but because @chrislaurita posted it, I’m posting it too! 😘🥰

GIFT IDEA! This is one of my favorite beauty tools for anti-aging and treatment of acne! Dr. Dennis Gross DRX SpectraLite FaceWare Pro Masque LED! Only 3 minutes a day! My skin never looked better! More even skin tone and very clear! I’ve been using it for about 3 months and I’m obsessed with it!  @drdennisgross #Antiaging #acne #giftideas

Just a catch up and a Happy New Years! I’m grateful for all of you! Xoxo 
For those asking what color lipstick I was wearing… it wasn’t Charlotte Tillbury lipstick as I originally thought. I was wearing Pat McGrath Labs MatteTrance Omi 107!
Hair color questions ask @hairbytav ❤️

5 hour lunch! Lots to talk about. Lots of laughs too! Reunited and it feels so good!  NO,  I don’t want back on RHONJ! I live in Las Vegas and moving to Orange County in CA this summer! Although the Ultimate Girls trip sounds fun, I don’t have a sitter for that long to care for Nicholas to be able to do it right now. No, our friendship rekindling has nothing to do with our mutual disdain for Melissa. Teresa and I had a great friendship BEFORE the show and now that all the stress, toxicity, outside influences, and pressures from being on a show together are gone, and life is good for both of us, it is easier to forgive and maintain a friendship. It’s that simple. #NewBeginnings for REAL this time! Lucy and Ethel are BACK and living our BEST lives. Life is good! 👯‍♀️
Clearing up some rumors for you guys! 🤗❤️

My son CJ bringing me gorgeous flowers from him and @chrislaurita , and also @giarestivo (CJs girlfriend he’s known since the 5th grade) and @lina_alexis ! THANK YOU! I LOVE THEM! (For my birthday 4/26, I was given permission to post a pic of C.J. 🤗❤️) #grateful Thank you all for your beautiful DM’s and well wishes. I appreciate you!
It was so nice visiting with @kathywakile and @richardwakile and all their sweet friends at the pool at the @encorebeachclub @wynnlasvegas #cabana and #coctails #BeautifulDay  Always a pleasure! 🤗❤️

My Nicholas did a Q & A with his S2C teacher @tompkinsvaleri in his @s2clasvegas  session. He’s been doing so well and starting to open up! It’s truly life changing! If you have any questions regarding how Spelling to Communicate (S2C) works, please reach out to either tag above to find out! If you haven’t seen the movie Spellers yet, I suggest you get a box of tissues and watch it! 😭 You can find it on Spellersthemovie.com. It’s mind blowing! Also, read the book “Underestimated, An Autism Miracle “ by JB Handley and his son Jamison! Nick spelled out recently to my family, “Spelling has changed my life, it has freed me from a silent prison.” If you know a non- speaking individual, please look into to S2C!

Happy Mothers Day to all of you loving Mothers out there! I hope you enjoyed a very special day today with those you love. I had a great brunch today with the fam! (I am also loving my new eggplant @clarasunwoo liquid leather jacket! Thank you! Xoxo) 💐🤗💕🥂🍾😁🫶🏼 P.S. I have the best Mom ever! I feel blessed.
We did a practice run the night before the hurricane/tropical storm, Hilary. Only 15 jars! We finally found San Marzano tomatoes that deliver right to your door! We are ready for more bushels! ❤️😋🍝🍅🫙

It’s always entertaining and educational listening to @temple_grandin and attending @tacanow conferences, especially with friends! I love @tacanow’s new #autism workbook! Great job! 😃👍🏼👍🏼 Visit TACA’s website for more info! https://tacanow.org/.

October included Fire Prevention Week. Kitchen safety is so important! Make sure you follow these tips to keep safe. Thank you @AARBF and @pecs_usa @pecsglobal for creating these important visuals. Nick is going to practice them all! @alisongresenclark
